00:09:00.239 --> 00:09:06.719
Two things you will notice about this data is some of these values have quite different ranges.

00:09:07.359 --> 00:09:12.000
So something like the area is in the order of hundreds of thousands, and something like

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:19.200
