00:09:20.239 --> 00:09:25.119
stale sensitivity, we need to deal with that. Additionally, we have a lot of these

00:09:25.679 --> 00:09:32.880
predictors being quite correlated. So generally, for most shapes, we have that the area, perimeter,

00:09:33.520 --> 00:09:38.719
